mainText: Belgium seized a suspected Russian shadow fleet tanker.
The United States reported no American casualties following strikes by Iran.

titleText: JTF News: BBC News, Deutsche Welle
mainText: A cargo plane crashed near La Paz, Bolivia, resulting in 15 deaths.
Iran states it has conducted strikes on a U.S. military base in Bahrain and launched strikes in the region.

titleText: JTF News: CBC News, ABC News Australia
mainText: Canadian Foreign Minister Chrystya Freeland urged all Canadians in Iran to shelter in place as the U.S. and Israel launched attacks.
